description: Erection of 2 residential blocks (17 and 19 storeys) connected at ground floor level comprising self-contained apartments, lower ground floor, flexible workspace (Use Class B1) on upper ground floor and roof top amenity, provision for car and cycle parking, refuse and associated communal spaces and hard and soft landscaping, subject to Deed of Agreement dated 01 April 2020 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.  This application is accompanied by an Environmental Statement.
site_name: Land, garages, alleyway rear of 416-444, High Road, Wembley, HA9
